title: Stade Montchaninois
text:
The <dfn>Stade montchaninois Bourgogne</dfn> is a French <a href="rugby%20union">rugby union</a> club founded in 1961 nowadays playing in regional championship of <a href="Bourgogne">Bourgogne</a>. 
In past play in the <a href="Top%2016">French Rugby championship, first division</a>
